&lt;unk&gt; and his brothers ( italian : &lt;unk&gt; e i &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1967 italian drama film directed by luchino visconti . the film is based on the novel of the same name by albert camus . the film was selected as the italian entry for the best foreign language film at the 58th academy awards , but was not nominated .